{
  "page": "Milk Snakes",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Milk Snakes</b> are one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_mountain_clans\" title=\"Vale mountain clans\">Vale mountain clans</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Mountains_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Mountains of the Moon\">Mountains of the Moon</a>, according to Archmaester <a href=\"/index.php/Arnel\" title=\"Arnel\">Arnel</a>'s <i><a href=\"/index.php/Mountain_and_Vale\" title=\"Mountain and Vale\">Mountain and Vale</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Milk_Snakes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Milk_Snakes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Lharys\" title=\"Lharys\">Lharys</a> claims it was either members of the Milk Snakes or the <a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Brothers\" title=\"Moon Brothers\">Moon Brothers</a> that were the first to descend upon <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a>'s party in the <a href=\"/index.php/Mountains_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Mountains of the Moon\">Mountains of the Moon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Milk_Snakes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After the mountain clans are armed by <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a>, the Sons of the Mist wield steel swords and mail hauberks, watching the <a href=\"/index.php/High_road\" title=\"High road\">high road</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a> and threatening travelers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Milk_Snakes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Vale.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_31\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 31\">Chapter 31</a>, Tyrion IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_65\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 65\">Chapter 65</a>, Arya XII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403213616\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.014 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.015 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 284/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8626/1000000\nPost‐expand in